				\begin{document}$$\:\widehat{R}$$\end{document}, tree depth, energy, divergent transitions, and trace plots) indicated no problems during sampling [23]. For visualization of the associations, additionally quartiles of UFP, LDSA, NO2 and ozone levels were computed, and the percent changes of outcome measures together with their 95% confidence intervals were plotted as a function of these quartiles.
